---
title: Thai-Spiced Tofu & Saucy Coconut Noodles with Crushed Peanuts
description: This fragrant meal packs oodles of flavour into every mouthful. With Thai spices on the tofu and aromatic makrut lime leaves in the coconut sauce, plus crunchy crushed peanuts to top it all off, this beats takeaway hands down.
